{{#partial "content"}}
    {{#if uniqueId}}
        <div id="returning-agent">
            <h2 class="text-center"><u>Welcome back, {{uniqueId}}</u></h2>

            <h4><b>Here's an overview of your registry</b></h4>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-3"><p>Heroes Registered: {{totalHeroes}}</p></div>
                <div class="col-md-3"><p>Squads Present: {{totalSquads}}</p></div>
                <div class="col-md-3"><p>Heroes w/ squads: {{squadfullHeroes}}</p></div>
                <div class="col-md-3"><p>Heroes without squads: {{squadlessHeroes}}</p></div>
            </div>

            <div id="newsFeed">
                <h2 class="text-center"><u>NEWS</u></h2>
                <h4><b>Gotham News Report</b></h4>
                <p>We denounce with righteous indignation and dislike men who are so beguiled and demoralized by the
                    charms of pleasure of the moment, so blinded by desire, that they cannot foresee the pain and
                    trouble that are bound to ensue; and equal blame belongs to those who fail in their duty through
                    weakness of will, which is the same as saying through shrinking from toil and pain. These cases are
                    perfectly simple and easy to distinguish. In a free hour, when our power of choice is untrammelled
                    and when nothing prevents our being able to do what we like best, every pleasure is to be welcomed
                    and every pain avoided. But in certain circumstances and owing to the claims of duty or the
                    obligations of business it will frequently occur that pleasures have to be repudiated and annoyances
                    accepted. The wise man therefore always holds in these matters to this principle of selection: he
                    rejects pleasures to secure other greater pleasures, or else he endures pains to avoid worse
                    pains</p>

                <h4><b>The Night Rises</b></h4>
                <p>More GCPD push order to keep a better eye on abandoned warehouses and deserted amusement parks. Says
                    Commissioner Gordon, "We have an alarming number of places that can operate as secret hideouts"</p>

                <h4><b>Anonymous encrypted text. From who though?</b></h4>
                <p>Dignissim sodales ut eu sem integer vitae. Aliquet enim tortor at auctor. Integer quis auctor elit
                    sed vulputate mi sit amet mauris. Leo vel fringilla est ullamcorper eget. Varius sit amet mattis
                    vulputate. Amet risus nullam eget felis eget nunc. Morbi tristique senectus et netus. Dui vivamus
                    arcu felis bibendum ut. Aliquet nec ullamcorper sit amet risus nullam. Quis enim lobortis
                    scelerisque fermentum dui faucibus."</p>

                <h4><b>Alfred's Messages</b></h4>
                <p>Master Bruce, please remember to take a bath!</p>
                <p>P.S: Your bat suits are in the laundry machine, you might want to avoid fighting crime tonight unless
                    you choose to wear Robin's outfit</p>

            </div>

        </div>
    {{else}}
        <div id="session-form">
            <h3 class="text-center">New agent detected, please let us know who you are....</h3>
            <form action="/success" method="post">
                <label for="uniqueId">Agent Name</label>
                <input type="text" id="uniqueId" name="uniqueId" class="form-control"
                       placeholder="How do you want to be referred to as?">
                <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Save</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    {{/if}}

{{/partial}}

